---
const IMAGE_SRC = "/SMS-Web/about/placeholder.jpg"; // placeholder (put any image here)
const IMAGE_ALT = "Association of Mathematical Sciences club photo (placeholder)";
---

<section class="bg-[#fef8ec] dark:bg-[#003049]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 sm:py-18">
    <header class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl text-[#003049] dark:text-[#fef8ec] sm:text-4xl">
        About
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-[#fef8ec]/80">
        A brief overview of the Association of Mathematical Sciences.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Club photo -->
    <div class="mt-10">
      <figure class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-3 shadow-sm dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-white/10">
        <!-- themed border frame -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#c1121f]/40 bg-[#fef8ec] p-2 dark:border-[#fef8ec]/30 dark:bg-[#003049]">
          <img
            src={IMAGE_SRC}
            alt={IMAGE_ALT}
            loading="lazy"
            class="aspect-video w-full rounded-xl object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-[#fef8ec]/70">
          Club photo (placeholder)
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-5">
    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-[#fef8ec]/80">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed euismod, nulla sit amet
        tincidunt laoreet, turpis arcu bibendum purus, a interdum sapien urna a nisi. Integer
        ac velit sed risus accumsan tincidunt.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-[#fef8ec]/80">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin fermentum, urna at
        consequat placerat, lorem arcu cursus nisl, et ultricies metus libero sit amet turpis.
        Donec vitae odio ut libero vestibulum bibendum.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-[#fef8ec]/80">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur vel sem at mauris
        convallis facilisis. Nam euismod, arcu sed pulvinar interdum, velit elit viverra magna,
        at vulputate justo mi a magna.
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
